    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the CFD hemolysis model meets the minimum threshold for regulatory submission under the current evidence package. Despite multiple credibility factor gaps, the available validation evidence for pressure-head and hemolysis index at two operating points is considered sufficient for the intended use. This determination is recorded as Accepted for package closure purposes.",
